column2: SELECT TOP # gsi.z, gsl.oiii_#_flux, gsl.oiii_#_flux_err, gsl.nii_#_flux, gsl.nii_#_flux_err, gsl.h_alpha_flux, gsl.h_alpha_flux_err, gsl.h_beta_flux, gsl.h_beta_flux_err, p.objId, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.expAB_r, p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i FROM Galaxy as p JOIN galSpecLine AS gsl ON p.specobjid = gsl.specobjid JOIN galSpecInfo AS gsi ON p.specobjid = gsi.specobjid WHERE gsl.oiii_#_flux > # AND gsl.nii_#_flux > # AND gsl.h_alpha_flux > # AND gsl.h_beta_flux > # AND gsl.oiii_#_flux/gsl.oiii_#_flux_err > # AND gsl.nii_#_flux/gsl.nii_#_flux_err > # AND gsl.h_alpha_flux/gsl.h_alpha_flux_err > # AND gsl.h_beta_flux/gsl.h_beta_flux_err > #
